# Tailwind Styling

All styling via `className` + Tailwind utilities. Merge conditionals with
`cn()` from `@/lib/utils`. Use theme vars (`text-foreground`, `bg-muted`,
`border-border`) and arbitrary values (`w-[180px]`) for dynamic sizes.

## Prohibited

- `style={{ ... }}` inline objects
- CSS-in-JS (emotion, styled-components, …)
- Component-level `.css` / `.scss` files (global `index.css` is fine)

## Examples

```tsx
// ❌
<div style={{ padding: 8, background: '#fff' }}>
<span style={{ color: selected ? '#6366f1' : '#e2e8f0' }}>

// ✅
<div className="p-2 bg-background">
<span className={cn("text-xs", selected ? "text-indigo-400" : "text-border")}>
```
